--   health      : health points (hospitals etc.)
--   education   : education points (schools)
--   power       : power supplied (+) or consumed (-)
--   water       : water supplied (+) or consumed (-)
--   color       : BrickColor name for the building pad
--   icon        : emoji shown in UI
--   description : flavour text

